{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/building-digital-uk/about/complaints-procedure","content_id":"8037060f-5684-4021-a9b3-109b6fe6dabb","description":"Building Digital UK (BDUK) became part of the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology (DSIT) in November 2025 and now follows the department's complaints procedure. ","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>BDUK became part of DSIT in November 2025. For guidance on how to raise a complaint, see <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-science-innovation-and-technology/about/complaints-procedure\">Complaints procedure - Department for Science, Innovation and Technology</a>.</p>\n\n<p>All other correspondence for the attention of BDUK should be sent to <a href=\"mailto:correspondence@dsit.gov.uk\">correspondence@dsit.gov.uk</a> and we will aim to provide a response within 20 working days.</p>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"Contact email addresses updated.","public_timestamp":"2024-04-24T12:43:56Z"},{"note":"Updated to reflect BDUK moving from DCMS to DSIT. ","public_timestamp":"2024-01-12T14:00:29Z"},{"note":"Updated to reflect BDUK as an executive agency. ","public_timestamp":"2022-09-26T09:10:59Z"},{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2022-06-10T15:44:00Z"}],"organisation":"120a16f4-37db-451d-9034-a9038a5c65f4","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"complaints_procedure","first_published_at":"2022-06-10T16:44:00+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/building-digital-uk/about/complaints-procedure","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/building-digital-uk/about/complaints-procedure","base_path":"/government/organisations/building-digital-uk/about/complaints-procedure","content_id":"8037060f-5684-4021-a9b3-109b6fe6dabb","document_type":"complaints_procedure","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-04-24T12:43:56Z"